      "description": "Offered is a mechanically-sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The chassis remains rigid, utilizing a M-Variable Differential Lock for superior traction. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline with excellent compression. It is a driver-focused machine with a precise shift linkage and a suspension setup that maintains original geometry and damping characteristics.",
