      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss and has been frequently waxed, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid, typical of careful road use. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean; the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one, and the leather seats are in great shape with only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All features, including the heated seats, navigation system, and sunroof, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has a documented service history, including a recent fluid flush and a fresh set of tires with plenty of tread remaining. The engine pulls strongly and the transmission shifts through all gears seamlessly. This is a reliable, honest car that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
